data.title: NFL, Fantasy Football, and NFL Draft
data.meta_description: The latest football news, analysis, and rankings from PFF. Featuring player grades, rankings and stats for the NFL, fantasy football, and NFL Draft.
data.text:
The Best of PFF showcases newly published or timely PFF stories that deserve your attention.

Mon, 19 Aug 24 21:00:45 +0000

By Mark Chichester Aug 19, 2024 5:00 pm EDT

Stanford wide receiver Elic Ayomanor exploded onto the scene with a record-breaking performance against Colorado, racking up 294 yards and three touchdowns in the second half and overtime. His standout season earned him a spot on the PFF Big Board, where he ranks among the top returning receivers in the Power Five. With his relentless drive and support system behind him, Ayomanor is poised for an even bigger season in 2024.
